			<text>They briefly scan your ship and inform you that you are not "properly equipped" for this type of mission.</text>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Leave them alone. [ Nil ]</text>
		<event>
			<text>If they wanted your help they would surely ask for it. You prepare to leave.</text>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="teleporter" lvl="1">
