		<text>Your fearless crew easily overcome the intruder, but the Rebel ship still needs to be dealt with. [ Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>Attempting to deal with attacks from inside and out is never easy! [ 1 Human Boarder, Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
