			<text>Reluctantly accept his proposal and fight the Rebel ship. [ -3 Hull, Rbl SF DR, Fleet+ | -3 Hull, 2 Human Boarders, Rbl SF DR | (Visible) x3 HumanCrew+, Defector Quest, Rbl SF DR | 1 HumanBoarder, Rbl SF DR, Crew- (CB+) ]</text>
			<event load="ALISON_DEFECTOR_HELP_2"/>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<text>Reject him outright and execute him on the spot. [ Rbl SF DR; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
			<event/>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<text>Reject his offer again. [ Rbl SF DR, 1 Human Boarder; S: 0.5, 2-3, RStuff; Esc: 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
			<event>
				<boarders min="1" max="1" class="human"/>
			</event>
		</choice>
	</event>
